ar but without success; because of the\nrelationship between mass-loss rate and the halo surface brightness, not even\nan upper limit on the stellar mass-loss rate can be determined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2007 18:16:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
